('40000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002','How Microsoft Excel Skills Can Improve Office Productivity','excel-skills-office-productivity','Even basic spreadsheet skills can save time and improve accuracy in everyday administrative work.','Microsoft Excel is widely used for lists, calculations, budgets and basic reporting. Learning how to format spreadsheets, use common formulas and organise data can make routine office work faster and more accurate.

